opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 16th day of September 2004, the above-captioned appeal was improvidently granted and is hereby DISMISSED. Furthermore, Appellees’ Motion to Dismiss for Mootness is hereby DENIED.
Justice EAKIN did not participate in this matter.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
